索尔福德的伊斯灵顿工厂因附近的开发而“未来再次处于危险之中” https://www.nme.com/news/music/salfords-islington-mills-future-in-jeopardy-once-again-over-nearby-development-3816928?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=salfords-islington-mills-未来再次因附近的发展而陷入危险Laura MolloyThu, 28 Nov 2024 20:10:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3816928 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们将继续捍卫我们在这个社区的存在”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/salfords-islington-mills-future-in-jeopardy-once-again-over-nearby-development-3816928">后索尔福德的伊斯灵顿工厂因附近的开发而“未来再次陷入危险”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>索尔福德的伊斯灵顿工厂表示，由于附近的开发项目，其未来“再次处于危险之中”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchester-night-day-cardiff-fuel-post-lockdown-noise-complaints-venues-3103934">封锁后的噪音投诉威胁着曼彻斯特的夜场和日间场馆 - 但他们并不孤单</a></strong></li></ul><p>在上周（11 月 19 日）分享的 Instagram 帖子中，音乐场所的代表解释了索尔福德市议会最近批准在该地区建造 90 套经济适用房的计划对他们产生的影响。</p><p> “分享工厂最近发生的事情感觉非常及时，”他们写道。 “你们中的许多人可能已经注意到，在过去的几周里，心爱的 2 号单元已被拆除。</p><p> “这为索尔福德议会批准的建造 90 套经济适用房的计划铺平了道路，虽然我们确实支持整体住房的开发，但我们将继续捍卫我们在这个社区的存在！”他们说。</p><p>该场馆已经运营了26年，此前曾引起人们对未来当地居民潜在噪音投诉风险的担忧。据<a href="https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/whats-on/fears-future-salford-gig-venue-30343176" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《曼彻斯特晚报》</em></a>报道，音乐场馆信托基金还写信给该委员会，敦促他们采取措施防止这种情况发生。</p><p> “尽管在最近的一次小组听证会上表达了我们的担忧，索尔福德市议会还是批准了这一开发项目，”他们继续说道。 “这使我们作为音乐场所的未来再次处于危险之中。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCkAVM1N2op/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/20